1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,000
Emperor Yongning. Ten years on the throne. The Empress within, demon kings without — and no one at court can fight.

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:13,000
Three years in the cold palace — no outside contact, no one taught her combat?

3
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:19,000
Confirmed, Your Majesty. Only the lowest scullion eunuchs who delivered supplies.

4
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:25,000
Then how does a powerless girl become this? ...The way she looked at me — like a different person.

5
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:29,000
Your Majesty, may I say what I shouldn't.

6
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:32,000
The fever night she almost died. By morning — she was reborn.

7
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:37,000
I suspect — she is not the Lady Lin who entered this palace.

8
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:43,000
Her father Lin Huaiyuan once traveled south — among strange people. Perhaps he left her a way to survive.

9
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:50,000
The year she arrived, she was sixteen. She blushed every time she saw me — and her smile had two dimples.

10
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:56,000
The one I see now — is a blade reforged. Too sharp to hold.

11
00:00:56,000 --> 00:01:02,000
Keep watching her. Don't startle her. Report every move, every day.

12
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:07,000
[The hall doors close in silence — a candle pops — silence]

13
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:14,000
The Lady Lin in the cold palace — I find her pleasing. If you don't trust her, use her first.

14
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:19,000
Lin Wan'er, Lin Wan'er — what kind of person are you, really?

15
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:26,000
If Lady Lin shows treasonous intent — Captain of the Imperial Guard is to execute on the spot.

16
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:34,000
I can grant you power. I can take it back. Do not — disappoint me.
